### 2. Offer Helper — Shared Price Calculation Logic

#### [NEW] [offer.helpers.ts](file:///home/moataz-fawzy/Downloads/ssfasp/apple-store-main/BE/src/modules/admin/offer.helpers.ts)
Shared utility functions:
- `calculateDiscountedPrice(originalPrice, discountType, discountValue)` → number
- `applyOfferToCategory(category, offer, productRepo)` — updates all products in a category
- `revertOfferFromCategory(category, productRepo)` — sets `price = originalPrice` for all products in category (only if no other active offer exists)

