### 3. Admin Service — Offer Logic

#### [MODIFY] [admin.service.ts](file:///home/moataz-fawzy/Downloads/ssfasp/apple-store-main/BE/src/modules/admin/admin.service.ts)

**[createOffer](file:///home/moataz-fawzy/Downloads/ssfasp/apple-store-main/FE/js/admin-dashboard.js#228-316)**: After saving the offer, call `applyOfferToCategory()` to discount all existing products in that category.

**[deleteOffer](file:///home/moataz-fawzy/Downloads/ssfasp/apple-store-main/FE/js/admin-dashboard.js#317-331)**: After deleting the offer, call `revertOfferFromCategory()` to restore `price = originalPrice` for all products.

**`updateProduct`**: The incoming `price` from the frontend is treated as `originalPrice`. Recalculate discounted `price` if an active offer exists for the product's category.

